<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
    <head>
    <%- include("../fragmente/head.ejs") %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/resurse/scss/custom.css">
    </head>
    <body>
    <%- include("../fragmente/header.ejs") %> 
    <main>
        <!-- ETAPA 5: Task customizare boostrap -->
        <div class="container my-4">
            <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                    <h2>Despre Noi</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="lead">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Illo illum officia quidem consectetur deleniti suscipit eaque culpa vero maiores voluptatibus, sit corporis exercitationem, alias reprehenderit delectus nesciunt, magni maxime autem!</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary">Afla mai multe</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary">Contacteaza-ne</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- ETAPA 5: Bootstrap dark theme -->
            <div class="card mb-4 shadow" data-bs-theme="dark">
                <div class="card-header bg-secondary">
                    <h3>Serviciile Noastre</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Enim consectetur beatae id placeat dignissimos ipsam numquam asperiores iste esse. Nam quam possimus voluptates a rerum quibusdam dignissimos. Dignissimos, delectus velit.</p>
                    
                    <!-- ETAPA 7: Button group Bootstrap -->
                    <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Basic example">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Personalizare</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Livrare rapida</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Garantie</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- ETAPA 5: Alert dismissible Bootstrap -->
            <div class="alert alert-info alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                <h4 class="alert-heading">Stiai ca?</h4>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Harum amet voluptatum suscipit, illum tenetur quis quae quidem odio neque similique sit possimus, doloremque consequatur sed beatae laborum odit adipisci nihil.</p>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            
            <!-- ETAPA 5: Grid system Bootstrap -->
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Echipe de club</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Avem tricouri pentru toate echipele mari din ligile europene.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-secondary">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Echipe nationale</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Echipamente oficiale pentru echipele nationale din toata lumea.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-success">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Customizare</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Servicii de personalizare pentru orice tricou cumparat de la noi.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- ETAPA 5: Accordion Bootstrap -->
            <div class="accordion mt-4" id="accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h4 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            Livrare si Retur
                        </button>
                    </h4>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Informatii despre politica de livrare si retur.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h4 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            Garantie
                        </button>
                    </h4>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Informatii despre garantia produselor.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script> 
    <%- include("../fragmente/footer.ejs") %> 
    </body>
</html>